= IRE, at http://www.i-r-e.org/


=Description=

IRE promotes the diffusion of new economic thinking and alternative economic models, and it enforces multi-actor networks committed to these goals. Its main focus is currently on financial reform and monetary innovation, sustainable value chains, solidarity based initiatives and territorial economy.  


